data.description: Peace and quiet of country living on 5 acres MOL in Mustang Schools! This updated 3 bedroom 2 bath home featuring fresh paint and new floors with an open floor plan, oversized laundry room and tons of storage space inside and several outbuildings outside. There is a 24'x30' shop is insulated with cement floor, 24x30' pole barn, chicken coop and storm shelter.
